lead_paragraph: Dale Steyn and JP Duminy led South Africa to a thrilling two-run win over Group One rivals New Zealand on Monday that kept them in the hunt for a semi-final spot at the World Twenty20 in Bangladesh.

headline.main: Steyn and Duminy Steer South Africa to Thrilling Win
